Bumpy Roads, No Worries: Don’t let bumps or turns affect your phone. The strong lock and gel suction cup keep your phone steady on rough roads. To reuse, simply rinse with warm water and wipe clean. Built to Last: Made from scratch and shock-free ABS material, the Portronics Clamp M3 Car Windshield and Dashboard Mobile Holder promises durability and longevity.
